  "body": "This will probably be the biggest 2.1 feature: we want to publish our testing suite on the npm package, along with helpers, behaviors, etc., so users can more easily and correctly test their code. A lot of work is required before this can be achieved though:\r\n\r\n - [ ] Add a testing guide (#1077)\r\n - [ ] Improve test descriptions (#1157)\r\n - [x] Test the helpers (https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/issues/1078)\r\n - [x] Improve the EVM exception helpers (https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/issues/942)\r\n - [x] Improve the logging helpers (#1026)\r\n - [ ] Set standards for our behaviors and document them (https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/issues/1085) \r\n",
